</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>LifeSmart ColoLight MIX 智能量子燈，隨意拼接組成個人化燈飾</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/13/lifesmart-cololight-mix-smart-light/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=lifesmart-cololight-mix-smart-light</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Edward]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 13 Dec 2021 07:45:33 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[家居無線]]></category><category><![CDATA[燈飾]]></category><category><![CDATA[ColoLight MIX]]></category><category><![CDATA[lifesmart]]></category><category><![CDATA[智能量子燈]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1074512</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>一年一度的聖誕節快要來到，未知大家是否已開始著手裝飾家中，以迎接這個普天同慶一年一度的歡樂節日？如果還沒有，又 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>一年一度的聖誕節快要來到，未知大家是否已開始著手裝飾家中，以迎接這個普天同慶一年一度的歡樂節日？如果還沒有，又想有簡單增加節日氣氛的方法，透過燈飾改變氣氛就是最容易及直接的方案了。LifeSmart 最近推出的 ColoLight MIX 智能量子燈，應該可以幫到大家。</p><h2>隨意拼接組成個人化燈飾</h2><p>ColoLight MIX 最特別的地方，就是它傳承了量子燈一貫靈活輕巧的拼接設計，用家可按個人喜好，透過專用的連接片及 ColoLight Mix Extension，就可以拼接多盞量子燈並組合供電，以組成大家心目中喜歡的個人化燈飾圖案。另外，每盞 ColoLight MIX 都可展示多達 1,600 萬種顏色，只要透過 ColoLight App，就可以轉換量子燈的顏色、亮度、色調，甚至可透過 App 內多款預設的主題式炫彩動態效果，或者自定義不同呼吸燈效果、色彩改變速度及方向等，令燈飾變化萬千。這樣，大家就可以按不同節日改變智能量子燈的效果，以營造出不同的節日氣氛。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_14.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074550" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_14-694x434.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_14-694x434.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_14-1280x800.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_14-768x480.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_14-1536x960.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_14.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>設定簡單供電容易</h2><p>上文亦有提及，只需要透過簡單的零件，就可以將多盞智能量子燈組合在一起，而拼接方式亦十分容易，只需要插上特定的連接片，就可以將 ColoLight MIX Extension 接通。另外，每盞 ColoLight MIX 智能量子燈中都內置了 18650 電池，接通後只要將接駁了電源的 USB-C 線連接至其中一盞量子燈，就可為組合多達 8 塊的量子燈充電，而量子燈背亦支援磁吸功能，又或者可使用附送的 3M 貼，無論大家是想貼在金屬櫃，又或者牆上都沒有問題，令擺放位置的彈性大大提升。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_6-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074551" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_6-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_6-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_6-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_6-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_6-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_6-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_6-2048x2048.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_6-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_10-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074552" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_10-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_10-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_10-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_10-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_10-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_10-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_10-2048x2048.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/ColoLight-MIX_10-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><h2>使用容易用 App 可遙距控制</h2><p>每款 ColoLight MIX 量子燈都內建了 37 顆 LED 燈，只需要輕按量子燈上的按鈕，就可以開關燈光、切換工作模式（動態 / 單色 / 聽音模式），而在燈亮時只需要點擊按鍵即可切換燈效，又或者長按 5 秒重置 MIX 並進入配對狀態。另外，用家只要將 ColoLight MIX 智能量子燈與 ColoLight App 配對好，就可以在流動裝置上，就量子燈進行遙距控制或作出時間排程，令量子燈可配合用家的作息時間或上班時間作智能開關，既可智能省電，亦可用擔心忘記關燈而浪費電力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_13-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074553" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_13-592x580.jpg" alt="" width="592" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_13-592x580.jpg 592w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_13-918x900.jpg 918w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_13-768x753.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_13-1536x1506.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_13-2048x2008.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Scene_13-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 592px" /></a></p><p><strong>LifeSmart ColoLight MIX </strong><strong>智能量子燈功能簡介</strong></p><ul><li>多方位隨意拼接  光彩更細膩動人</li><li>1600 萬種顏色呼吸燈  多款主題式炫彩動態效果</li><li>收音律動，自定隨聲變色效果\</li><li>磁吸 / 3M 貼上牆</li><li>電池 / USB-C 供電 (ColoLight MIX 主燈)</li><li>ColoLight App (iOS /Android) 遙距控制  時間排程</li></ul></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=8yx5ZJZJXOM:-yq9ukelG3s:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=8yx5ZJZJXOM:-yq9ukelG3s:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>GMK Xpanel2 達到 Delta E&lt;2 規格，便攜螢幕一樣有高色彩精準度</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/13/gmkmonitorxpanel24k/notebook/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=gmkmonitorxpanel24k</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 13 Dec 2021 07:39:13 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Notebook 配件]]></category><category><![CDATA[流動電腦]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1074936</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>以往便攜螢幕設計主要是以娛樂或是文書的副螢幕為主，很多用家只希望螢幕有更鮮豔的色彩表現，又或是可以 4K 高解 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>以往便攜螢幕設計主要是以娛樂或是文書的副螢幕為主，很多用家只希望螢幕有更鮮豔的色彩表現，又或是可以 4K 高解像度運作，以追求更細膩的字型表現就能滿足需要。但隨更多專業級用家開始使用便攜螢幕協助工作，色彩的準確度就慢慢變得重要。而 GMK 最新推出的 Xpanel2 4K 螢幕，更做到 Delta E &lt; 2 規格，更接近影像原生色彩。</p><h2>Delta E 是什麼？</h2><p>色彩精準度顧名思義，就是指顯示設備顯示的色彩精準程度，一般用 Delta E 或 ΔE 來表示。 Delta E 代表螢幕色彩和標準值之間的差距，數值越小越好，代表更佳的色彩還原能力，當數色越大就表代表失真情況更為嚴重。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/lab-sphere2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1074949" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/lab-sphere2.jpg" alt="" width="596" height="525" /></a></p><p>當 Delta E 在 1.6 &#8211; 3.2 之間時，人眼基本看不出色彩的差異，大部分時間都會被為是相同的顏色。所以專業級螢幕一定 Delta E 都會在 3 以下。而在 Delta E 3.2 &#8211; 6.5 時，一般情況下使用不會有任何問題，顏色失真程度仍在可接受的範圍內，一般主流螢幕都是在這個區間。如果然 Delta E 進一步增大，就會有明顯的失真情況，亦是大家常對顏色失準的產品。</p><h2>Delta E&lt;2 達專業級質素</h2><p>總括而言，想選擇一隻專業級螢幕，Delta E&lt;3 是必須的，而 Delta E&lt;2 已經是專業級螢幕的規格範圍。而 Delta E&lt;6 就是正常可以接受的極限，會有明顯失真的情況。</p><h2>Delta E&lt;2 專業級規格</h2><h2>GMK Xpanel2 4K</h2><p>GMK Xpanel2 主打專業用家市場，用上 4K@60Hz IPS 面板，而且在顏色上更落足功夫，支援 Adobe 100% 色域之餘，更擁有 Delta E&lt;2 的頂級規格。而且對於很多執相用家關心的對比度部分，更支援至 1500:1，同時由於擁有 600 nit，足以應付大部分的室外使用環境，更適合需要在不同環境下工作的用家。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074938" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-3-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-3-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-3-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-3-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-3-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-3.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲包裝內配件十分齊全，提供了兩條支援 HDMI 輸出的 Type-C to Typc-C 線、USB A to C 線以及 HDMI ，另外更有 USB-C OTG 線，方便用家透過螢幕的 USB 連接鍵盤等週邊。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074939" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-5-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-5-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-5-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-5-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-5-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-5.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲機身採用倒 V 型支架，不單可以無段式改變角度，最大更可增開至 90 度。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-6-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-6-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-6-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-6-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-6-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-6.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲USB-C 影像及電源的雙插頭為通用設計，只要接上會自動偵測接口種類。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-7.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074941" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-7-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-7-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-7-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-7-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-7-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-7.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲倒 V 底座明顯更為穩固，就算是在交通工具等不平穩的地方使用亦更安心。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-8.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074942" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-8-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-8-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-8-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-8-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-8-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-8.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲因為主要控制器在後方支架內，所以機身可以做到超薄，而且造工亦可以更為精細。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-9.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1074948 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-9-516x900.png" alt="" width="516" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-9-516x900.png 516w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-9-333x580.png 333w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-9-768x1339.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-9-881x1536.png 881w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-9-1175x2048.png 1175w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-9.png 918w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 516px" /></a>▲無段式調校令角度更自由</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-12.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074943" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-12-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-12-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-12-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-12-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-12-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-12.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲在 Windows 中直接支援 Touch 功能。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-13.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074944" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-13-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-13-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-13-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-13-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-13-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-13.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲超薄式邊框設計。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-14.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074945" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-14-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-14-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-14-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-14-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-14-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-14.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲內置自動偵測方向功能，轉直時會自動改變 Windows 顯示方式。亦可以在選單中設定轉向角度。</p><h2>剪片執相更放心</h2><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-15.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1074946" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-15-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-15-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-15-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-15-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-15-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gmk-15.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>如果你對顏色準確度有高要求，GMK Xpanel2 就可以完全滿足你需要。而且倒 V 型座底角度多變之餘更支加穩陣，適合在不同環境下使用。而且如果你用的 Macbook 又或是支援 Thunderblot 4 接口的裝置，更只需要單一 USB 線即可完成影像傳輸及供電之用，令使用更加方便</p><p>更多資料可以睇官方網站：<a href="https://bit.ly/31htOSu">https://bit.ly/31htOSu</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
